CHEATSHEET

--> Keybinds
--> SUPER = Windows / Cmd key <--

SUPER + F12 : Open this cheatsheet

--> Essential
SUPER + T    : Open kitty (terminal)
SUPER + R    : Open rofi (app menu)
SUPER + E    : Open nemo (file manager)
SUPER + Q    : Close active app
SUPER + M    : Quit Hyprland
SUPER + F    : Toggle floating / fullscreen for active app
SUPER + L    : Lock screen
SUPER + T    : Change wallpaper

--> Workspaces
SUPER + (1 -> 9)                        : Move to workspace (1 -> 9)
SUPER + ARROW                           : Move window focus in arrow direction
SUPER + CTRL + ARROW                    : Move window in arrow direction
SUPER + SHIFT + (1 -> 9)                : Move window to workspace (1 -> 9)
SUPER + SHIFT + ARROW (left / right)    : Move to workspace left / right
SUPER + S                               : Move to special workspace
SUPER + SCROLL                          : Move through active workspaces
SUPER + LCLICK                          : Move active window
SUPER + RCLICK (at window edge)         : Resize floating window

